the Philadelphia Daily News.
   Keyes, 42, succeeds Thomas E. Livingston, who was appointed to
the new post of director of business development.
   ``She's a terrific journalist and will bring a great deal to the
Daily News,'' said Editor Zachary Stalberg, who announced the
