Orlando (Fla.) Sentinel since 1985. She has also worked for
Louisville (Ky.) Courier-Journal and The Tennessean in Nashville.
   Prior to joining the Tennessean in 1976, Keyes taught English
for five years at Fisk University.
   Livingston, 39, will work with the advertising department to
develop new sources of revenue, Stalberg said.
  
